<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>課後回饋問卷｜找到你的色彩 · 質穎形象顏究室®</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@300;400;500&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --almond: #EDE3D8;
    --cream: #F7F3EE;
    --warm-white: #FAFAF8;
    --parch: #F4EFE8;
    --charcoal: #2C2C2C;
    --bark: #6B5C4E;
    --muted: #7A756F;
    --ink-lite: #9A8F86;
    --border: #DDD8D0;
    --highlight: #F0EAE1;
    --orange: #C97B4B;
    --orange-light: #D9A07A;
    --error: #B85C4A;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--almond);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ─── Header ─── */
  .site-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D08A5C 0%, #C97B4B 55%, #B5663A 100%);
    color: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .site-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 25% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,0.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 90%, rgba(91,46,20,0.25) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .brand-mark {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .site-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .site-header p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .site-header .org-line {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .deco-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin: 1.25rem auto;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ─── Progress ─── */
  .progress-wrap {
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .progress-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .progress-bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 2px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 2px; }
  .progress-bar-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--orange); border-radius: 2px; width: 0%; transition: width 0.5s ease; }
  .progress-pct { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--orange); min-width: 32px; text-align: right; }

  /* ─── Main ─── */
  .main { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 5rem; }

  /* ─── Section Headers ─── */
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 1.75rem; }
  .section-header:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
  .section-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--orange-light); line-height: 1; min-width: 2rem; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.05rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--charcoal); }
  .section-sub { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.15rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* ─── Question Card ─── */
  .q-card { background: var(--warm-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1.75rem 1.75rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .q-card:focus-within { border-color: var(--orange-light); }
  .q-label { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .q-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--orange); letter-spacing: 0.1em; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .required { color: var(--error); margin-left: 0.15rem; }

  /* ─── Star Rating ─── */
  .star-scale { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .star-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .star-labels { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .rating-btn {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: transparent; border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .rating-btn:hover { border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--orange); background: var(--highlight); }
  .rating-btn.selected { background: var(--charcoal); border-color: var(--charcoal); color: var(--cream); }

  /* NPS 0-10 */
  .nps-row { display: flex; gap: 0.35rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .nps-btn {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: transparent; border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .nps-btn:hover { border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--orange); background: var(--highlight); }
  .nps-btn.selected { background: var(--charcoal); border-color: var(--charcoal); color: var(--cream); }
  .nps-labels { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.4rem; }

  /* ─── Radio / Checkbox ─── */
  .options-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .option-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; user-select: none;
  }
  .option-item:hover { border-color: var(--orange-light); background: var(--highlight); }
  .option-item.selected { border-color: var(--charcoal); background: var(--highlight); }
  .custom-dot {
    width: 18px; height: 18px; min-width: 18px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 1px; position: relative; transition: all 0.15s; background: white;
  }
  .option-item.selected .custom-dot { border-color: var(--charcoal); background: var(--charcoal); }
  .option-item.selected .custom-dot::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: white; border-radius: 50%;
    top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
  .custom-box {
    width: 18px; height: 18px; min-width: 18px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px;
    margin-top: 1px; position: relative; transition: all 0.15s; background: white;
  }
  .option-item.selected .custom-box { border-color: var(--charcoal); background: var(--charcoal); }
  .option-item.selected .custom-box::after {
    content: '✓'; position: absolute; color: white; font-size: 11px; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%); line-height: 1;
  }
  .option-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--charcoal); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Age range grid */
  .age-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; }
  @media (max-width: 480px) { .age-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .other-input {
    width: 100%; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding: 0.4rem 0; border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: transparent; font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--charcoal); outline: none;
  }
  .other-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }
  .other-input:focus { border-bottom-color: var(--orange); }

  /* ─── Textarea ─── */
  textarea {
    width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--charcoal); background: white;
    resize: vertical; min-height: 90px; line-height: 1.8; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  textarea:focus { border-color: var(--orange-light); }
  textarea::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }

  /* ─── Conversion highlight card ─── */
  .convert-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--highlight) 0%, var(--cream) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--orange-light);
  }
  .convert-badge {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--orange); border: 1px solid var(--orange-light);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* ─── Consent ─── */
  .consent-box { background: var(--highlight); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .consent-options { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .consent-btn {
    flex: 1; min-width: 120px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: white;
    border-radius: 2px; font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s;
    color: var(--charcoal); text-align: center;
  }
  .consent-btn:hover { border-color: var(--orange); }
  .consent-btn.selected-yes { background: var(--charcoal); border-color: var(--charcoal); color: white; }
  .consent-btn.selected-no { background: white; border-color: var(--muted); color: var(--muted); }
  .consent-items { list-style: none; margin: 0.75rem 0 0; }
  .consent-items li { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); padding: 0.2rem 0; padding-left: 1rem; position: relative; }
  .consent-items li::before { content: '·'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--orange-light); }

  /* ─── Submit ─── */
  .submit-wrap { margin-top: 3rem; text-align: center; }
  .submit-btn {
    background: var(--charcoal); color: var(--cream); border: none; padding: 1rem 3rem;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover { background: var(--orange); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }
  .submit-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.6; cursor: default; }
  .submit-note { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

  /* ─── Thank You ─── */
  .thank-you { display: none; text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 5rem; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .thank-you.show { display: block; }
  .ty-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--orange); }
  .ty-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .ty-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.9; }
  .ty-brand { margin-top: 2.5rem; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--orange-light); text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* CTA box in thank you (conversion) */
  .ty-cta-box {
    display: none;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ty-cta-box.show { display: block; }
  .ty-cta-eyebrow { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--orange-light); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .ty-cta-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .ty-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--orange); color: white; padding: 0.85rem 2.2rem;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif; font-size: 0.92rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .ty-cta-btn:hover { background: var(--orange-light); }
  .ty-cta-sub { font-size: 0.74rem; color: rgba(247,243,238,0.5); margin-top: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* ─── Validation ─── */
  .error-msg { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--error); margin-top: 0.4rem; display: none; }
  .q-card.has-error { border-color: var(--error); }
  .q-card.has-error .error-msg { display: block; }

  .section-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 2rem 0; }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .rating-btn { width: 40px; height: 40px; }
    .nps-btn { width: 34px; height: 34px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .nps-row { gap: 0.25rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Header -->
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="brand-mark">質穎形象顏究室® · Floral Way Image Studio</div>
  <div class="deco-line"></div>
  <h1>找到你的色彩 · 課後回饋問卷</h1>
  <p>關於今天的課程，希望妳可以幫忙寫下這份問卷</p>
  <p class="org-line">臺中市政府社會局　主辦　·　靜宜大學　協辦</p>
</header>

<!-- Progress -->
<div class="progress-wrap">
  <span class="progress-label">填寫進度</span>
  <div class="progress-bar-bg"><div class="progress-bar-fill" id="progressFill"></div></div>
  <span class="progress-pct" id="progressPct">0%</span>
</div>

<!-- Form -->
<main class="main" id="surveyForm">

  <!-- Section 0 -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">·</span>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">基本資料</div>
      <div class="section-sub">幫助我們了解今天參與課程的妳</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-age">
    <span class="q-num">基本資料</span>
    <div class="q-label">妳的年齡區間是？<span class="required">*</span></div>
    <div class="age-grid" id="age-options">
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="18以下" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">18 以下</span></label>
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="18-24" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">18–24</span></label>
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="25-34" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">25–34</span></label>
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="35-44" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">35–44</span></label>
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="45-54" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">45–54</span></label>
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="55-64" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">55–64</span></label>
      <label class="option-item" onclick="selectRadio(this,'age')"><input type="radio" name="age" value="65以上" style="display:none"><span class="custom-dot"></span><span class="option-text">65 以上</span></label>
    </div>
    <div class="error-msg">請選擇年齡區間</div>
  </div>

  <hr class="section-divider">

  <!-- Section I -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">I</span>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">課前 vs 課後的轉變</div>
      <div class="section-sub">找到適合自己的顏色，清晰程度的改變</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-q1">
    <span class="q-num">Q 01</span>
    <div class="q-label">上課<strong>前</strong>，你對「個人色彩」的了解程度是？<span class="required">*</span></div>
    <div class="star-scale">
      <div class="star-row" id="q1-row">
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q1',1)">1</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q1',2)">2</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q1',3)">3</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q1',4)">4</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q1',5)">5</button>
      </div>
      <div class="star-labels"><span>完全不了解</span><span>非常了解</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="error-msg">請選擇一個分數</div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-q2">
    <span class="q-num">Q 02</span>
    <div class="q-label">上完課<strong>後</strong>，你對「個人色彩」的了解程度是？<span class="required">*</span></div>
    <div class="star-scale">
      <div class="star-row" id="q2-row">
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q2',1)">1</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q2',2)">2</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q2',3)">3</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q2',4)">4</button>
        <button type="button" class="rating-btn" onclick="selectRating('q2',5)">5</button>
      </div>
      <div class="star-labels"><span>完全不了解</span><span>非常了解</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="error-msg">請選擇一個分數</div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-q3">
    <span class="q-num">Q 03</span>
    <div class="q-label">上完這堂課，你覺得自己<strong>最大的改變</strong>是什麼？<span class="required">*</span></div>
    <textarea id="q3" placeholder="請用自己的話分享……" oninput="updateProgress()"></textarea>
    <div class="error-msg">請填寫這題</div>
  </div>

  <hr class="section-divider">

  <!-- Section II -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">II</span>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">認知翻轉</div>
      <div class="section-sub">哪一個內容讓你最有感？</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-q4">
    <span class="q-num">Q 04</span>
    <div class="q-label">這堂課最讓你印象深刻、<strong>顛覆原本想法</strong>的是？（可複選）</div>
    <div class="options-list" id="q4-options">
      <div class="option-item" data-value="顏色不是只分冷色暖色這麼簡單" onclick="toggleCheckbox(this,'q4')"><span class="custom-box"></span><span class="option-text">原來顏色不是只分「冷色系／暖色系」這麼簡單</span></div>
      <div class="option-item" data-value="網路測驗不一定準" onclick="toggleCheckbox(this,'q4')"><span class="custom-box"></span><span class="option-text">網路上的「30秒測出你的季節」其實不一定準</span></div>
      <div class="option-item" data-value="顏色沒有禁區只有適合的版本" onclick="toggleCheckbox(this,'q4')"><span class="custom-box"></span><span class="option-text">顏色沒有「禁區」，只有屬於自己的版本</span></div>
      <div class="option-item" data-value="親眼看到專業測色的真實變化" onclick="toggleCheckbox(this,'q4')"><span class="custom-box"></span><span class="option-text">親眼看到專業測色在臉上的真實變化</span></div>
      <div class="option-item" data-value="other-q4" id="q4-other-item" onclick="toggleCheckbox(this,'q4')">
        <span class="custom-box"></span>
        <span class="option-text">其他：<input type="text" class="other-input" id="q4-other-text" placeholder="請填寫……" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" oninput="updateProgress()"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-q5">
    <span class="q-num">Q 05</span>
    <div class="q-label">有沒有哪一刻，讓你有「<strong>原來是這樣！</strong>」的感覺？</div>
    <textarea id="q5" placeholder="分享你的 aha moment……" oninput="updateProgress()"></textarea>
  </div>

  <hr class="section-divider">

  <!-- Section III -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">III</span>
    <div>
      <div class="section-title">最有感的收穫</div>
      <div class="section-sub">這堂課，哪一句話最打中你？</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="q-card" id="card-q6">
    <span class="q-num">Q 06</span>
    <div class="q-label">上完課後，你覺得<strong>幫助最大的是</strong>？<span class="required">*</span></div>
    <div class="options-list" id="q6-options">
